      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented mapping between experimental and simulation input parameters; equivalency demonstrated for all parameters within stated uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency mapping between bench-test and simulation input parameters has been documented. Rotational speed and flow rate were nominally matched, but fluid rheology, hematocrit, and temperature equivalency were not formally established. Factor is not assessed."
    }
